include "helpers.fr"

# T12L acceptance #1: pure-modules library. Two words exposed,
# `test-pure.greet` returns 42 and `test-pure.shout` doubles its
# input. Together they exercise basic word definition + a library-
# internal include of helpers.fr.

to test-pure.greet [ 42 ]

to test-pure.shout with n [ doubled: n ]
